{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/spring-restapi-02.md/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"mvc-모텔이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mvc-%EB%AA%A8%ED%85%94%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"mvc 모텔이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MVC 모텔이란?</h3>\n<p>Model, View, Controller의 약자이다.</p>\n<p>Model - 어플리케이션 계층의 정보, 데이터 의미 (데이터베이스)<br>\nView - 화면 출력 로직을 담당 (HTML, 프론트)<br>\nController - Model과 View의 연결을 제어하는 로직<br>\n<br>\nSpring은 MVC모델을 사용하기 때문에 Model과 Controller를 생성해 API를 만들 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"model-패키지-생성하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#model-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"model 패키지 생성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Model 패키지 생성하기</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/29114/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/efc66/1.png 885w,\n/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/c83ae/1.png 1180w,\n/static/62ca7135de930dcde298f12e3a38820d/29114/1.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\nNew - Package를 통해 model 패키지를 생성해준다.\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/29114/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/fcda8/2.png 590w,\n/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/efc66/2.png 885w,\n/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/c83ae/2.png 1180w,\n/static/c295828a7206a4151046a331b0bed15f/29114/2.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n패키지 안에 우리의 데이터의 모델이 될 UserProfile 클래스를 하나 생성해준다.\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/29114/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/fcda8/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/12f09/3.png 148w,\n/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\n/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/fcda8/3.png 590w,\n/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/efc66/3.png 885w,\n/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/c83ae/3.png 1180w,\n/static/1cf51b0e663e7441be2ff8ddb1bf24c3/29114/3.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> phone<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> address<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>클래스에 데이터베이스에 저장할 변수를 정의해준다.<br>\n그리고 마우스 오른쪽클릭 - Source - Generate Constructor using Fields 를 통해 생성자를 선언해준다.\n<br><br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/29114/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/fcda8/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/12f09/4.png 148w,\n/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\n/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/fcda8/4.png 590w,\n/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/efc66/4.png 885w,\n/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/c83ae/4.png 1180w,\n/static/a6db74ea6219c5a371e367e1b5f54c53/29114/4.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n마찬가지로 Generate Getters and Setters를 통해 변수들의 getter, setter를 선언해준다.\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/29114/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/fcda8/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/12f09/5.png 148w,\n/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\n/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/fcda8/5.png 590w,\n/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/efc66/5.png 885w,\n/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/c83ae/5.png 1180w,\n/static/6439b761ab865c5cdf7af643b93c7775/29114/5.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\nUserProfile.Java 전체 소스코드\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/29114/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/fcda8/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/12f09/6.png 148w,\n/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/e4a3f/6.png 295w,\n/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/fcda8/6.png 590w,\n/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/efc66/6.png 885w,\n/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/c83ae/6.png 1180w,\n/static/8087b851b92b98aeca555bbab2a7f409/29114/6.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n다음은 Model과 마찬가지로 Controller 패키지를 생성해주고 그 안에 UserProfileController를 생성해준다.\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/29114/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/fcda8/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/12f09/8.png 148w,\n/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/e4a3f/8.png 295w,\n/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/fcda8/8.png 590w,\n/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/efc66/8.png 885w,\n/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/c83ae/8.png 1180w,\n/static/996f727eda4f50360bcba77c445e2ffd/29114/8.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n아직 Mysql을 연동하지 않았기 때문에 로컬테스트를 위해 Map을 선언하고 데이터를 추가한다.\n<br>\n스프링은 어노테이션(@)를 통해 해당 메소드의 역할을 지정해줄 수 있다.\n<br><br>\n@RestController - 해당 클래스가 Controller라는 것을 인식하게 함.\n<br>\n@PostConstructor - Controller클래스가 생성되면 처음으로 실행되는 메소드를 지정.\n<br>\n@GetMapping - 괄호안의 주소를 Get방식으로 데이터를 보내겠다는 뜻.\n<br>\n@PathVariable - 주소에 포함된 {} 안의 변수를 받아오겠다는 뜻.\n<br><br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/29114/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"9\"\n        title=\"9\"\n        src=\"/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/fcda8/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/12f09/9.png 148w,\n/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/e4a3f/9.png 295w,\n/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/fcda8/9.png 590w,\n/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/efc66/9.png 885w,\n/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/c83ae/9.png 1180w,\n/static/c50851b63cb834360aca3c190824513a/29114/9.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n프로젝트를 실행해 주소로 접속해보면 1번째 데이터가 Json형태로 잘 나오는 것을 알 수 있다.\n<br>\n다음엔 데이터 추가, 수정, 삭제에 대해 다뤄보자.","excerpt":"MVC 모텔이란? Model, View, Controller의 약자이다. Model - 어플리케이션 계층의 정보, 데이터 의미 (데이터베이스)\nView - 화면 출력 로직을 담당 (HTML, 프론트)\nController - Model과 View의 연…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-02.md/#mvc-%EB%AA%A8%ED%85%94%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\">MVC 모텔이란?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/spring-restapi-02.md/#model-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Model 패키지 생성하기</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/spring-restapi-02.md/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring을 통한 REST API 예제 - 02","date":"Mar 07, 2021","tags":["Springboot"],"keywords":["MojitoBar","Ju dongseok"],"update":"Mar 07, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/spring-restapi-02.md/","series":[],"lastmod":"2021-03-07"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}